sentence: In early trading on Tuesday, shares of Nike topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 0.7%.
Year to date, Nike registers a 15.6% gain.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is Home Depot, trading down 3.6%.
Home Depot is showing a gain of 6.6% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are Caterpillar, trading down 3.4%, and Cisco Systems, trading up 0.5% on the day.
